---
description: Amul Notify structure-aware development rules
globs:
  - '**/*'
alwaysApply: true
---

Read `AGENTS.md` first. It is the canonical guide for this repository.

Use the existing project layers:

- Commands in `src/commands`, actions in `src/actions`, wizards in
  `src/wizards`, and registration in `src/bot.ts`.
- Business logic in `src/services`, external clients in `src/libs`, models in
  `src/models`, and small helpers in `src/utils`.
- Runtime env belongs in `src/env.ts` and `.env.example`.

Do not edit generated `dist` output. Preserve callback payload stability,
strict TypeScript guards, secret handling, and the Telegraf middleware ordering
documented in `AGENTS.md`.
